        }
      ],
      "updated": 1781537776855,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\nFor each block hash:\n   |\n   +--> Fibonacci hash chooses shard\n   |\n   +--> lookup blockHash in that shard\n   |\n   +--> get HostBitmap\n   |\n   +--> learn which pods have that block\n\ncheck if any entries exist:\n   return the cached pod\nelse :\n    add hash to the index\n    mark the pods as empty\n     \n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\nFor each block hash:\n   |\n   +--> Fibonacci hash chooses shard\n   |\n   +--> lookup blockHash in that shard\n   |\n   +--> get HostBitmap\n   |\n   +--> learn which pods have that block\n\ncheck if any entries exist:\n   return the cached pod\nelse :\n    add hash to the index\n    mark the pods as empty\n     \n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
